\thispagestyle{empty}

\begin{abstract}
   The purpose of this note is to provide an overview of the containment
   problem for symbolic and ordinary powers of homogeneous ideals,
   related conjectures and examples. We focus here on ideals with
   zero dimensional support. This is an area of ongoing active research.
   We conclude the note with a list of potential promising paths
   of further research.
\keywords{symbolic power, fat points, Waldschmidt constants}
\subclass{MSC 14C20 \and MSC 14J26 \and MSC 14N20 \and MSC 13A15 \and MSC 13F20}
\end{abstract}



